title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: You may feel too large and wild to fit comfortably in a tame or routine existence today. The vivifying Libra New Moon accentuates your 9th House of Expansion and Adventure, triggering a current bout of wanderlust. Of course, taking a class or planning a long-distance trip could satisfy your spirits hunger for growth and new frontiers, but you might not be able to make your escape just yet. Enlist a friends help if you want to make faster headway; you increase your joint chances for success by strategizing together and encouraging each others dreams. Your focus determines your direction. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
